---
title: Glazed Peri Peri Chicken Breast with Herby Chips and Zesty Green Beans & Peas
description: This Glazed Peri Peri Chicken Breast is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
